---

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Our Core Services</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
        <p>Custom model development, MLOps pipelines, and LLM integrations to unlock strategic insights.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Cloud Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>Design and deployment of secure, scalable cloud environments for GovCloud, Azure, AWS, and hybrid.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Cybersecurity & Compliance</h3>
        <p>Zero Trust architecture, risk assessments, and federal compliance (CMMC, FedRAMP, NIST).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">DevOps & Automation</h3>
        <p>CI/CD pipelines, infrastructure as code, and container orchestration using modern best practices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">IT Modernization</h3>
        <p>Legacy system transformation, API enablement, and digital workflows tailored to mission-critical needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">24/7 Managed Support</h3>
        <p>On-demand support, monitoring, and SLA-backed services designed for high availability and uptime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
